<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmat kūrmmapurīśiturbhbhagavataḥ kāruṇyavārāṁnidhērvvi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṣṇōrnnīlaśilāmayaṁ suruciraṁ prāsādamabhraṁkaṣaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="3"/>cakrē ya stirucuṭṭumālyabhavanaṁ śrīkāryyamā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ścaryyakaṁ vīraśrīmadanaṁggabhīmanṛpatēssanmānapātrā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>graṇīḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrītī<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ttapādadāsasyatasya putrasya bhāminī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nṛsiṁhvabhaṭṭō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pādhyāya sarvvakratusuyājinaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē śarabiṁddu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>sūryagaṇitē vaiśākhamāsē sitē pakṣē kūrmmapurīśi 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>turbhbagavatō dīpārtthamācaṁdrabhaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tadbhāṁḍaukasi māḍa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>paṁcaka madāt śrīmatpirāṭyaṁbikā bhaktijñānavivṛddha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yē haripadadvaṁdvapadēpi śriyaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

